      "cookedHtml": "<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/4/346824137c3c2442a74b14fdc3d435f82dcc7d30.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/4/346824137c3c2442a74b14fdc3d435f82dcc7d30_2_690x120.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"120\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1785×313 40.1 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>can somebody help me with the formula?<br />\ni need Total hours in decimal</p>"
